name: Skriware 2
pre_gcode:
G90 ;absolute positioning
M82 ;set extruder to absolute mode
M420 S1 Z0.7 ;enable bed levelling
G1 Z10 F250 ;move the platform down 10mm
M107 ;fan off
M42 P11 S255 ;turn on front fan
M140 S{material_bed_temperature}
M104 T0 S{material_print_temperature, 0}
M104 T1 S{material_print_temperature, 1}
G1 F2500 Y260 X0
M190 S{material_bed_temperature}
M109 T0 S{material_print_temperature, 0}
M109 T1 S{material_print_temperature, 1}
M60 ;enable E-FADE Algorithm
M62 A ;filament sensor off
G92 E0 ;zero the extruded length
T1
G92 E0;zero the extruded length
G1 F300 Z0.3
G1 F1200 X20
G1 F1200 X180 E21 ;extrude 21 mm of feed stock
G1 F1200 E11
G1 F300 Z1.5
G92 E0 ;zero the extruded length again
T0
G92 E0 ;zero the extruded length
G1 F1200 Y258
G1 F300 Z0.3
G1 F1200 X40 E21 ;extrude 21 mm of feed stock
G1 F1200 E11 ;retracting 10 mm
G1 F300 Z1.5
M63 A ;filament sensor reset
M61 A ;filament sensor on
G92 E0 ;zero the extruded length again
M58 ;end of Start G-Code and signal retract management
T{initial_extruder_nr}
